## üìã Project Overview

**Purpose:** Track all projects in `/Users/eriksjaastad/projects` workspace and surface status, health, and resource usage.

**Architecture:**
- **Scanner:** Discovers projects, READMEs, TODOs
- **Database:** SQLite storage for project metadata
- **CLI:** Typer-based command interface
- **Dashboard:** Web UI (Flask) for visualization

**Key Features:**
- Auto-discovery of projects from filesystem
- External resource tracking (from project-scaffolding/EXTERNAL_RESOURCES.md)
- TODO status monitoring
- Last activity tracking

